===== Host =====

This class is designed to work with hosts. 

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:host:object#host|Host]]
  * [[manual:api:reference:host:object#host_inventory|Host inventory]]

Available methods: \\

  * ''[[manual:api:reference:host:create|host.create]]'' - creating new hosts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:host:delete|host.delete]]'' - deleting hosts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:host:get|host.get]]'' - retrieving hosts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:host:massadd|host.massadd]]'' - adding related objects to hosts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:host:massremove|host.massremove]]'' - removing related objects from hosts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:host:massupdate|host.massupdate]]'' - replacing or removing related objects from hosts
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:host:update|host.update]]'' - updating hosts